comment:
* This class allows the control of ADB-related functions that should only be called from the system
 * server.
 *
 * @hide Only should be called from the system server.

methods.name: public abstract void registerTransport(IAdbTransport transport)
methods.comment:
* Registers a ADB transport mechanism.
     *
     * @param transport ADB transport interface to register

methods.name: public abstract void unregisterTransport(IAdbTransport transport)
methods.comment:
* Unregisters a previously registered ADB transport mechanism.
     *
     * @param transport previously-added ADB transport interface to be removed

methods.name: public abstract boolean isAdbEnabled(byte transportType)
methods.comment: * Returns {@code true} if ADB debugging is enabled.

methods.name: public abstract File getAdbKeysFile()
methods.comment: * Returns the file that contains all of the ADB keys used by the device.

methods.name: public abstract File getAdbTempKeysFile()
methods.comment: * Returns the file that contains all of the ADB keys and their last used time.

methods.name: public abstract void notifyKeyFilesUpdated()
methods.comment:
* Notify the AdbManager that the key files have changed and any in-memory state should be
     * reloaded.
